data.description: Welcome to Sol Vista, a highly coveted neighborhood nestled along the western edge of Westminster, a stone's throw from Seal Beach and Huntington Beach. This home is an entertainer's dream. The heart of this residence is an oversized gourmet kitchen with an extra-large island and ample storage. Kraftmaid cabinets, Thermador stainless steel appliances, including a Double Oven, warming oven, 5 burner stove top, 42-inch built-in refrigerator, and pot filler, adorn the kitchen. A stack stone fireplace and walk-in pantry enhance the charm. The living, kitchen, and dining areas flow seamlessly into a tranquil backyard oasis featuring an in-ground pool, an outdoor barbecue, a sunlit grassy area, and shaded spaces beneath two motorized patio covers. This home boasts pride of ownership with lavish upgrades, including fresh paint inside and out, double pane Milgard windows, and upscale vinyl siding. With upgraded bathrooms, plank tile and refinished wood flooring throughout, smooth ceilings, LED recessed lighting, crown molding, and new lighting and fans. A first-floor bedroom and half bath provide practicality and comfort for family or overnight guests. Conveniently located just south of the 405 freeway, a mere 10-15 minutes from world class beaches, lively downtown areas, shopping, farmers markets, Seal Beach, Long Beach, 2nd Street, and highly rated schools of Huntington Beach. Don’t miss the opportunity to own in one of the most desirable neighborhoods in Orange County!
